==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Saturday
<hw>Sat"ur*day</hw> <pr>(?; 48)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>Saterday</ets>, AS. <ets>Saeterdaeg</ets>, <ets>Saeterndaeg</ets>,
<ets>Saeternesdaeg</ets>, literally, Saturn's day, fr. L.
<ets>Saturnus</ets> Saturn + AS. <ets>daeg</ets> day; cf. L. <ets>dies
Saturni</ets>.]</ety> <def>The seventh or last day of the week; the day
following Friday and preceding Sunday.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Saturity</ent>⟦br⟧
